rall, our results suggest a slightly greater rate of net stand\u2013level change than was reported by Phillips\n              et al\n              . Considering the spatial and temporal scale of sampling and associated studies showing increases in forest growth and stem turnover, the results presented here suggest that the total biomass of these plots has on average increased and that there has been a regional\u2013scale carbon sink in old\u2013growth Amazonian forests during the previous two decades.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Malhi, Y.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Phillips, O. L.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Baker, Timothy R.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Phillips, Oliver L.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Malhi, Yadvinder", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Almeida, Samuel", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Arroyo, Luzmila", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Di Fiore, Anthony", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Erwin, Terry", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Higuchi, Niro", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Killeen, Timothy J.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Laurance, Susan G.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Laurance, William F.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Lewis, Simon L.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Monteagudo, Abel", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Neill, David A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "N\u00fa\u00f1ez Vargas, Percy", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Pitman, Nigel C. A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Silva, J. Natalino M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "V\u00e1squez Mart\u00ednez, Rodolfo", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/2590b0c1b8ec031fc8bf4911db9599e3", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/dc579654ba013c16cede665f0421180346728bcdb5922c03e2d4b21bbeeb2642", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://s